start by installing dependancies: 
npx create-react-app my-app --template @chakra-ui
install carousel from react-responsive carousel
install react-router-dom 


What is Chakra UI?
Chakra UI is a simple, modular and accessible component library that gives you the building blocks you need to build your React applications.

Use different functions of chakra UI and carousel to make the website development more easy.

The main advantage of Chakra UI is that there is no need to make a seperate file for CSS,SCSS which consume less memory and more computation.



